# Serialization — RCD1 Format

## Principle
- Minimize tokens in prompts
- Use file references, not inline content
- Delta encoding for updates
- Bitsets for checklists

## RCD1 Messages
- `!S|pid|rev|ph|tb|cur|ts` — snapshot
- `!A|pid|rev|tid_list|m|k` — assignment
- `!D|pid|base_rev|new_rev|cur|ts` — delta

## Records (in snapshot)
- `F|fid|role|h=xxxx` — blob/file reference
- `M|mid|task_list|h=xxxx` — milestone
- `T|id|parent|deps|mid|ty|st|pr|rk|est|ctx|ac|ck|cr|lg` — task
- `I|idx|tid_list|op|err` — iteration history

## Delta Operations
- `U|tid|st|rev|err` — status update
- `R|tid_list` — mark ready
- `J|mid|tid_list|ok|meta` — milestone validation

## Task Status Codes
- 0: PENDING
- 1: READY
- 2: DONE
- 3: FAILED

## Rules
- NEVER include long text in prompts
- Reference specs by ID and hash
- Use deltas, not full snapshots, for updates
- External blobs for content >100 tokens
